<main class="flex min-h-screen flex-col justify-center px-6 sm:px-0">
    <h3 class="animate-fade-in mb-4 font-sfmono text-sky-400">
        Hola, <span>me llamo</span>

        <h1
            class="animate-fade-in font-calibre text-4xl font-semibold leading-none text-slate-50 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl"
        >
            Agustín Arnoldi.
        </h1>

        <h2
            class="animate-fade-in mt-2 font-calibre text-4xl font-semibold leading-none text-slate-400 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl"
        >
            Construyo cosas para la web
        </h2>

        <p class="animate-fade-in mt-2 max-w-md font-calibre text-slate-400 sm:max-w-lg sm:text-lg">
            Soy un desarrollador que busca superarse a diario. Interesado en vivir nuevas
            experiencias en el rubro tecnológico. Actualmente estudiando y aspirando a ser un gran
            programador de la nueva era.
        </p>

        <div class="mx-auto mt-16 flex h-12 w-12 md:mt-24 lg:mt-28 xl:mt-32">
            <a
                href="#about"
                aria-label="Ir a Sobre Mi"
                class="animate-fade-in animate-floating [&>svg]:hover:fill-sky-400"
            >
                <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    class="fill-white transition-colors duration-300"
                    width="48px"
                    height="48px"
                    viewBox="0 0 50 50"
                >
                    <g transform="translate(0,50) scale(0.1,-0.1)">
                        <path
                            d="M240 268 l0 -222 -45 44 c-24 24 -48 40 -52 37 -4 -4 19 -33 50 -65 l57 -57 57 57 c31 32 54 61 50 65 -4 3 -28 -13 -52 -37 l-45 -44 0 222 c0 141 -4 222 -10 222 -6 0 -10 -81 -10 -222z"
                        ></path>
                    </g>
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </h3>

    <style>
        h3.animate-fade-in {
            animation: fade-in 1s 0.25s both;
        }

        h3.animate-fade-in > span {
            animation: fade-in 1s 1s both;
        }

        h1.animate-fade-in {
            animation: fade-in 1s 2s both;
        }

        h2.animate-fade-in {
            animation: fade-in 2s 3s both;
        }

        p.animate-fade-in {
            animation: fade-in 2s 3s both;
        }

        a.animate-fade-in.animate-floating {
            transform: translateY(-15%);
            animation: fade-in 2.5s 3s both, floating 1.5s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes fade-in {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes floating {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(-15%);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(15%);
            }
        }
    </style>
</main>
